I thoroughly enjoyed this movie.  This was dubbed in English and there were no subtitles getting in the way, so I must have gotten a different version than some of the other reviewers.  The plot consists of a journey in search of a sword, with plenty of martial arts action, hostile natives, a giant snake, and betrayal(s). This was not the first time I've watched this movie, and probably not the last, either.  I highly recommend this to anyone who enjoys Oriental fantasy.

Very enjoyable and entertaining supernatural fantasy in the tradition of "Raiders of the Lost Ark."  High production values and a good story as usual from contemporary Chinese productions. And the special effects are just eye-poppingly good.  Well worth watching for an absorbing and entertaining evening of escape from reality.
